Prerequisite :
- git
- docker

Instructions to install git : https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-git-on-ubuntu-18-04-quickstart
Instructions to install docker : https://github.com/techcoreeasy/docker_demo


Step 1: git clone https://github.com/big-data-europe/docker-hadoop
        cd docker-hadoop/
Step 2: docker-compose up -d
Step 3: docker container ls
Step 4: docker exec -it namenode /bin/bash


